Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:48.69,Title,,0,0,460,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(640,480)}Batalha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Então os fracotes \Nestão trabalhando juntos...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:02:03.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que você conseguirá a chave \Ndas algemas em breve, não é, Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,O que diabos você está fazendo aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:15.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Vim para salvá-los.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:18.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Como vocês puderam cair em \Numa armadilha tão estúpida?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Como assim um atalho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:21.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Tamaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Ucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Desista, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não entende a sua situação...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Aguenta, Ucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Inúteis...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:58.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Qualquer um poderia matá-los assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:06.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Uns idiotas dizendo que vão me matar...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.93,Main,,0,0,0,,...estão fazendo um alvoroço lá fora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:10.57,Main,,0,0,0,,É incrível que você tenha encontrado...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,...aliados nessas circunstâncias.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:16.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa habilidade sua...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:20.43,Main,,0,0,0,,...é algo que respeito desde a Grande Guerra.{revisar nome}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:27.29,Main,,0,0,0,,...o próprio líder é um idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:30.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você o escolheu, Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:34.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Antes você era muito mais promissor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Até quando criança você era mais ousado...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:41.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...e mais esperto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou errado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.95,Main,,0,0,0,,...transformou você em um covarde?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Silêncio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:55.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu não quero ser como você!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu fui... salvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está falando do meu irmão, Corazón, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você se tornou um covarde,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,por que quer morrer em vão...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,...junto com esse idiota?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:17.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Não machuque o Chapéu de Palha-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Não toque nele!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.50,Main,,0,0,0,,O que diabos é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.83,Main,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo com o corpo dele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sabia, é um clone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Um clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma marionete de fios.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Galera...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:50.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Que bom que você está bem...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, vamos ajudar o Chapéu de Palha-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:57.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou seguro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:01.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, não, não, não...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:03.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, e essas pernas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:07.82,Main,,0,0,0,,A propósito, nós acabamos com o cara importante, não foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:12.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu já disse antes \Nque é um impostor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele se deu ao trabalho de \Nenviar a marionete de fios...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele queria zombar de nós?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Aquele cara de antes, Kelly Funk,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:24.40,Main,,0,0,0,,aquele desgraçado nos enganou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.48,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Que cara ingênuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:32.85,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ele caiu direitinho na nossa armadilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Nós descobrimos, mas quando \Ndecidimos pará-lo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:42.17,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Temos que fazer algo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.32,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Abdullah, você consegue se levantar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:58.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1022)}Aquele infame assassino, Kelly, caiu \Nem uma fração de segundo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:00.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Se isso é verdade,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,então, é como se aquele maldito \Ntivesse nos salvado!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está zombando de nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo lá fora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.60,Main,,0,0,0,,E o Cabbage e os outros?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Estamos ficando muito para trás...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:14.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Com certeza todos estão no segundo nível!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:18.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu pensei que isso era um atalho \Npara chegar ao campo de girassóis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Temos que voltar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:25.65,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(980,0)}PLANALTO DO PALÁCIO REAL - NÍVEL 1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}O que é isso...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uau! Nenhum caiu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:36.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...no primeiro nível!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:36.95,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(520,0)}PLANALTO DO PALÁCIO REAL - NÍVEL 2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.28,Main,,0,0,0,,É impossível!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:42.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Nossos subordinados não \Nconseguem lidar com eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha e os outros ainda não chegaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:48.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos acabar com eles um por um.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:52.53,Main,,0,0,0,,...Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.20,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:02.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, não! Vai ter outra!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:05.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Como vocês podem se assustar \Nse nem sabem o que é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:08.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Galera, não percam o inimigo de vista!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:12.15,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,400)\fad(200,200)}INTERIOR DO POÇO\N NÍVEL 1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:14.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele fez um atalho de verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:17.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Galera, cuidem do Ucy, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.21,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu gosto dessa confusão!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:24.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Chinjao e os outros estão indo para o terceiro nível!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Detenham eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse buraco enorme...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:30.19,Main,,0,0,0,,O que diabos está acontecendo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.98,Main,,0,0,0,,É o Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:58.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Rápido, Chapéu de Palha-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:58.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:02.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere aí, Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:06.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está falando sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:09.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:11.57,Main,,0,0,0,,É sério!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:14.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uns besouros não podem \Nfazer humanos voarem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:16.50,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,400)\fad(200,200)}ANTIGO PLANALTO REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vamos correr pela cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, sim! Eu gosto dessa ideia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, vou dar as instruções.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está nos ouvindo, pequeno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:28.10,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,370)\fad(200,200)}AEROLINHAS DE TONTATTA - TÁXI AMARELO {PACE ONLY}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:27.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Este é o Serviço de Salto \Nda Aerolinha Tontatta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:30.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Como as pessoas grandes pesam muito, \Nnão podem levá-los voando!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Viu? Nós avisamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:35.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Não temos muito tempo, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:35.94,Main,,0,0,0,,...vamos decolar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:36.80,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:49.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}Já dissemos que assim não vamos conseguir voar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:52.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Leo, não seja imprudente!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, vocês estão bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Malditos anões!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão pagar por isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou voando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:08.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles não podem fazê-los voar, \Nmas podem parar sua queda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:12.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou caindo, caindo, caindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Relaxe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Como vou relaxar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou me espatifar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Vá em direção a um telhado!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Um telhado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:24.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim! E pouse com cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora! Pule!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou voando!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:46.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Pular dos telhados\N os ajuda a se elevarem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:49.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Já estou me acostumando!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Muito bem! Você está indo muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Me sinto como se fosse um balão!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Cuidado com os ataques de baixo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:16.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Dirijam-se ao campo\N de girassóis do quarto nível!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:16.19,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(753,250)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,400)}CAMPO DE GIRASSÓIS - NÍVEL 4
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.22,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)}FRENTE À FÁBRICA DE SMILE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Fraland!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Temos uma ideia para abrir \Na porta da fábrica!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:38.34,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:40.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Então mantenha ele distraído!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:51.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Podem contar comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:58.05,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,390)\fad(200,200)}PARTE SUPERIOR DA\N ESTÁTUA DE PICA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Você acabou de pisar na minha espada!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.58,Main,,0,0,0,,E daí?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:21.56,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(625,415)\fad(200,200)}NA VILA\NSABO VS. FUJITORA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:18.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Que luta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:35.75,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(625,405)\fad(200,200)}PALÁCIO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ei, ei, Doffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:37.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Você enviou o Joker de linha para algum lugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:41.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu queria enviar algo, mas\N parece que ele não precisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Garotos...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Lembram do dia em que conhecemos o Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele era louco!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Até os olhos dele eram de um louco...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:57.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele se parecia comigo quando eu era pequeno...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu senti que ele se tornaria meu braço\N direito em mais ou menos dez anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:20.49,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma pena que eu tenha que\N matá-lo com minhas próprias mãos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:24.31,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Temos um intruso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.49,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não toquem nele!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:27.85,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ele tem explosivos amarrados ao corpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.03,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.72,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos é essa criança?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.37,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Quem deixou ele passar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:38.24,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Deixe-me me juntar à sua tripulação.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:41.81,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu quero destruir tudo que vejo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:45.08,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Cidades, casas, pessoas...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.82,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu quero destruir tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.60,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu cresci...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:52.82,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...na Cidade Branca, Flevance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:57.17,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não me resta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:01.76,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...muito tempo de vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:13.07,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,330)\fad(150,150)}DRESSROSA\NDENTRO DA GAIOLA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:26.33,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(500,0)}PALÁCIO REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:21.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora estou ficando sentimental...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:26.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Para que você veio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:32.33,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(400,0)}BELLAMY, A HIENA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:32.33,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(400,0)}PIRATA COM RECOMPENSA\N DE 195 MILHÕES DE BELIES
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Você matou o Chapéu de Palha, Bellamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:36.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você enviou Dellinger para me matar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa ordem realmente veio de você?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, era isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Você já não...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.58,Main,,0,0,0,,...espera mais nada de mim?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me faça dizer diretamente, Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:00.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Seu objetivo é diferente do meu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Há muito tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:07.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Você sempre quis ser um pirata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:10.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas eu não.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:13.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Qualquer coisa teria servido para mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Qualquer coisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Enquanto eu puder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.94,Main,,0,0,0,,...destruir este mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:29.91,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(550,0)}PLANALTO DO PALÁCIO REAL - NÍVEL 2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:29.91,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(550,0)}EXÉRCITO DO COLISEU VS. A FAMÍLIA DONQUIXOTE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:33.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Sai da frente, garoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou com pressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:38.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, o que você acha que eu sou?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, me diga, Suleiman, o Decapitador!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:51.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Você era carrasco na guerra, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:54.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu também adoro executar pessoas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:54.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Chutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Nossa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Que pena.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:15.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Já acabou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:30.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Lá vêm os oficiais da família!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:35.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:37.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu serei o primeiro a chegar ao terceiro nível!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.29,Main,,0,0,0,,O que são essas pedras que estão sobressaindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse lugar é perigoso...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:46.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Jirai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,...Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:53.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Vovô, já estou indo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Da-in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Flutua, flutua...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Juu-Ton Vise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:09.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês veem, idiotas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é o quão poderosos são\N os oficiais da família!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele conseguiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles não podem avançar mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Te peguei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:25.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Bukimorphose!{revisar}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Revolver Leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:37.39,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(400,0)}CIDADE AO SUL, SEVIO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu o peguei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Tragam as cordas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,E cuidem dele, ele levou um tiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Que os outros apaguem o fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:49.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:49.65,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:53.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu quase matei minha família!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Fui eu que incendeiei a cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:02.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu cortei meu amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu também!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é culpa deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:11.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo aconteceu por causa da influência de Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:14.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Temos que acabar com\N esse jogo de alguma forma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:16.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Encontramos o Rei Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:21.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está com o homem das\N cinco estrelas, o Deus Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Ótimo, vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas só os capturaremos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:28.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, se não fizermos isso, esse jogo\N continuará até que morramos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Primeiro, tomaremos como\N reféns o Rei Riku e o Deus Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:37.98,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,E atrairemos os outros\N criminosos usando esses reféns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.54,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Avisem todo o país!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Dirijam-se ao antigo planalto do rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.23,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:57.66,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:04.76,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(400,0)}FÁBRICA DE SMILE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:08.23,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,375)\fad(200,200)}INTERIOR
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles derrubaram aquele tanque de SAD?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:14.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Peguem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:16.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:17.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Houve um tremor repentino...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:21.31,Main,,0,0,0,,...e o tanque caiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que houve um tremor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Calem a boca! Vocês não precisam saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:27.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês não querem curar a doença\N da Princesa Mansherry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro que querem, não é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro que queremos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Como está a saúde dela?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:42.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:42.15,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:45.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Infelizmente, a princesa não \Nestá melhorando, de jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.40,Secondary,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:51.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor, deixem-nos ver a princesa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga! Vocês são muito chatos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Calem a boca e trabalhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:07.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiotas, parem de reclamar \Ne continuem produzindo Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:12.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Abram a porta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:14.99,Main,,0,0,0,,O que vocês estão fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:17.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu disse para trabalharem, idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:19.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Parem de ficar olhando para o nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês não me ouvem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:22.98,Main,,0,0,0,,por dentro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Essas palavras...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,São as abelhas rosas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Bian!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Inhel! Wicka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:44.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles nos viram, Bian!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Abelhas rosas, próxima mensagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Nós fomos enganados!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:58.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,"Nós fomos enganados"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:01.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Do que eles estão falando?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:03.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:05.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês não estão nos ouvindo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Nós fomos enganados?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:09.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Sobre a doença da princesa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:12.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo esteve nos enganando?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Lutem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:21.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que precisam de outra \Nsurra para entender as coisas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:24.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Não sei o que está acontecendo, mas \Numa coisa eu sei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Um companheiro nunca mente!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:32.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanshita!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:49.33,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(400,0)}PLANALTO DO PALÁCIO REAL - NÍVEL 2
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:03.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Você vai atrapalhar de novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:06.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Suba.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:10.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou dizendo que vou te levar porque\N não tenho outra opção!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Você quer chegar onde\N Doflamingo está o mais rápido possível, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Está bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Perfeito, vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Você já foi modesto alguma vez na vida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:24.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Que seja, se apresse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me dê ordens!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Farul!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:32.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Escute, se formos pegos pelos oficiais, \Nnão poderemos continuar avançando.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:34.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou cortar a parede e abrir caminho,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.54,Main,,0,0,0,,você cuida do resto dos inimigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:37.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:39.93,Main,,0,0,0,,E vamos direto para o terceiro nível...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei! Tem um a mais aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, Soldado!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:44.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando você subiu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:45.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Segui o caminho que o Luffyland abriu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:48.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Você seguiu longe demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ótimo! Estava te procurando!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:54.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que você seja amigo dele,\N estamos carregando peso demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:55.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Desça!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:58.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos encontrar com a Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca está em território inimigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:01.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você não a deteve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:02.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas escute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:06.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos encontrar no campo \Nde girassóis do quarto nível.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:09.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela também está na lista de criminosos!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela está com meus companheiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:13.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Escute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:14.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Meu querido cavalo, Farul,\N só cavalga bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,...com duas pessoas ou menos!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:19.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,O lombo do touro tinha mais espaço...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:23.10,Main,,0,0,0,,A propósito, velho, por que você desapareceu \Nantes que eu percebesse?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Não importa a situação, o que devo fazer é...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:30.77,Main,,0,0,0,,...acabar com Doflamingo e recuperar o país!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:33.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas tem mais uma coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:35.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Há um homem entre os\N oficiais supremos da família...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.63,0:22:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,...que quero matar com minhas\N próprias mãos, custe o que custar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Velho, você não está\N disposto a morrer, está?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.91,0:22:43.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Não diga bobagens!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:46.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Não serei derrotado na minha forma humana!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:47.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Então está tudo bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:48.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem nada, desça!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Então desça você!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:51.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Não diga besteiras!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:52.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é o pior!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Dá pra ver que você faz parte\N da Pior Geração!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Cuidado, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:57.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Olhe para frente, para frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:23:00.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me diga o que fazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:03.37,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Esses são...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:09.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Vá em frente, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:13.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Nós vamos distraí-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:16.65,Main,,0,0,0,,De repente...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.65,0:23:19.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Antes estavam desorganizados\N e brigavam entre si!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.72,0:23:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.92,Main,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu, pessoal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.53,0:23:26.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Dagama, o estrategista militar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.15,Main,,0,0,0,,E isso é guerra!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Se cada um fizer bagunça separadamente, ninguém vai chegar ao topo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:36.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu não confio em Dagama, mas \Nconcordo com o plano dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos parar os oficiais aqui e deixar o Chapéu de Palha avançar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:43.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixe isso com a gente e vá!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.77,0:23:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Certifique-se de levá-lo \Naté lá, Cavendish!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.75,0:23:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, eu não sou \No transporte público!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.75,0:23:53.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Temos que vencer esta guerra!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem feito!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.85,0:24:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que aquele cara está assumindo a liderança.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:08.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Que irritante!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:20.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Daruma!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.36,0:24:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas o que...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:26.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, me solta, maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.93,0:24:33.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Continue subindo, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.83,0:24:37.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Fogo, fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.70,0:24:39.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Não os deixem avançar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.30,0:24:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Biken!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.10,0:24:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Saint-Exupéry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.24,0:24:57.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.85,0:25:00.49,Main,,0,0,0,,...Jet Gatling!
